reviews.review_text: 4/19/82 awesome show.  some of my favorites are in this show. might as well sounds hot.  peggy-o is great as always.  they love each other is soon becoming a new facorite of mine. all i wanna know is where can i download?

cumberland etc unfortunately this SBD lacks bass as is fairly typical for the 1st half of 82 with a couple of exceptions. the SBD's from may onwards are generally better, much fatter bass, better mixes etc too bad as this is a GOOD show

the cumberland has a few moments but the one from the greeks in may is much better and better sounding. phil plays the intro bass and its well recorded and Garcia's play is really tasty. the vocals are good as well. the franklins is good but again lacks bass and as such is too bright
